Interface ReconfiguratorFunctions

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Reconfigurator

    public interface ReconfiguratorFunctions
    Author:
    arun A minimal interface defining reconfigurator server functions. This interface is implemented by Reconfigurator and must be implemented by any client or proxy for reconfigurators.
